        "subheading": "Every batch is slow-dried over hours, not minutes.",
        "lead": "<p>Good treats aren't manufactured — they're made. Slowly, in small batches, from food you'd recognise on your own cutting board. Here's exactly how a YumBud treat goes from whole ingredient to the piece your dog hears hit the bowl.</p>",
